high_descs: Turn left and go to the bath tub.
Pick up the bar of soap closest to you.
Turn around and go to the sink closest to the tub.
Rinse the soap in the sink.
Back away from the sink slightly.
Put the soap in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the bathtub
Pick up the soap bar from the bathtub
Turn around and walk back to the left bathroom sink
Rinse the soap bar under water in the sink and remove it
Walk back slightly from the sink then turn back to face the green trash bin
Put the soap bar in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned soap bar in the green trash bin

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the tub.
Pick up the closest bar of soap.
Turn right and take a step right to the sink.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Take a step to the left.
Place the soap in the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed bar of soap in a bin.
